- Derive from ffmpeg-7.spec
- Update to release 8.0
  * New features:
  * Native decoders (Packman builds): APV, ProRes RAW, RealVideo
    6.0, Sanyo LD-ADPCM, G.728
  * VVC decoder improvements: IBC, ACT, Palette Mode
